(23, 1, '2025-03-28 02:16:40', '2025-03-28 02:16:40', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Chiu 26/3/2025, ng y Trng i hc in lc t chc Hi ngh thc hin quy trnh cng tc nhn s Cp y&nbsp;i hi ng b ln th XXV (nhim k 2025 - 2030).</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>D Hi ngh, pha ng y Khi cc trng i hc, Cao ng H Ni c cc ng ch: ng Trn Anh Tun - U vin Thng v, Trng ban t chc ng y Khi; b Don Th Thu Hng - Ph chnh Vn phng ng y Khi; b L Hng Ly - y vin y Ban kim tra ng y Khi.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>V pha Trng i hc in lc c NGT.PGS.TS V nh Ng - B th ng y, Ch tch Hi ng trng; PGS.TS inh Vn Chu - Ph B th ng y, Hiu trng; PGS.TS. Nguyn L Cng - Ph Hiu trng; TS. Dng Trung Kin - Ph Hiu trng; cng cc ng ch trong Ban Thng v, Ban Chp hnh; B th, Ph B th cc chi b ca cc n v ca Nh trng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pht biu ti Hi ngh, NGT.PGS.TS V nh Ng qun trit ni dung, mc ch, quy trnh th tc, tm quan trng v  ngha ca Hi ngh. ng thi, bo co tng kt cng tc nhn s i hi nhim k 2020 - 2025; Phng hng cng tc nhn s i hi nhim k 2025 - 2030.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;y l Hi ngh quan trng v vic thc hin quy trnh cng tc nhn s Cp y, i hi ng b ln th XXV, nhim k 2025 - 2030. Qua  nhm pht huy tnh cng khai, dn ch v tr tu tp th trong vic la chn ngun cn b cho ng  b sung, xy dng i ng cn b lnh o, qun l ca Nh trng cho nhim k 2025 - 2030,... NGT.PGS.TS V nh Ng chia s.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ti Hi ngh, cc i biu  nu cao tinh thn trch nhim, cng tm, khch quan, nghin cu k tiu chun, iu kin  la chn, b phiu gii thiu nhn s ti c v ln u chc danh y vin Ban Chp hnh; y vin Ban thng v; B th ng y; Ph B th ng y; y vin y ban Kim tra ng y nhim k 2025 - 2030 theo ng quy nh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thng qua Hi ngh ny, nhm b sung hon thin quy trnh cng tc nhn s Cp y, i hi ng b ln th XXV, nhim k 2025 - 2030, gp phn to s ch ng v cng tc cn b nhn s ng trong nhim k; bo m tnh k tha, pht trin, gi vng on kt ni b v s n nh ca Nh trng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Chun b chu o cng tc nhn s cho i hi ng b Nh trng', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chuan-bi-chu-dao-cong-tac-nhan-su-cho-dai-hoi-dang-bo-nha-truong', '', '', '2025-03-28 02:16:42', '2025-03-28 02:16:42', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tintucedu/?p=23', 0, 'post', '', 0),
