(29, 1, '2025-03-28 02:25:37', '2025-03-28 02:25:37', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Va qua (21/3/2025), ti&nbsp;Trng i hc in lc (EPU) din ra l&nbsp;k kt hp tc gia Nh trng&nbsp;vi cc doanh nghip trong cng tc o to v&nbsp;cung ng ngun nhn lc cht lng cao.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>D chng trnh v&nbsp;pha cc doanh nghip c: B V Th Xun, Tng Gim c&nbsp;Cng ty C phn&nbsp;pht trin ngh nghip Tui tr Vit;&nbsp;Mr. Hirokazu Tanaka - Tng Gim c&nbsp;Cng ty CP Technobridge NKE; b Trng Th Nguyt, Tng Gim c&nbsp;Cng ty CP Lotus Human Resources.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nhm Cng tc v in v Nng lng thuc Din n Doanh nghip Vit Nam c ng John Rockhold, Trng nhm Cng tc in v Nng lng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>V pha Trng&nbsp;i din Trng i hc in lc c&nbsp;TS. Dng Trung Kin  Ph Hiu trng Nh trng;&nbsp;Ths.  Hu Ch - Gim c Trung tm Truyn thng v Quan h Doanh nghip;&nbsp;TS. Nguyn t Minh  Trng khoa Qun l cng nghip v nng lng;&nbsp;Ths. Chu Vn Tun  Quyn Gim c Trung tm Ngoi ng;&nbsp;&nbsp;cng i&nbsp;din cn b, ging vin mt s n v.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXcT24K8Z4aEHKjyF1HuZ8m8VA6c1j7h5Fy92RfRQmEtDPOWjBVix_b1wmwCZzGSPKX0A4blhBsXyNmJm-iCwG7EW-TaDn2s48OwgCbcXQina1EcqjA1Ub5RrXnBvSz9doBgjn8vyA?key=fKQJm8HDt4tBe727O_QarXFf\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>TS. Dng Trung Kin pht biu ti L k kt.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Gi li cm n ti cc i tc l doanh nghip, TS. Dng Trung Kin - Ph Hiu trng Trng i hc in lc&nbsp;chia s, vic hp tc vi doanh nghip khng ch mang li li ch trc tip cho sinh vin m cn c  ngha to ln i vi Nh trng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"S kin hm nay l minh chng r rng cho mi quan h hp tc cht ch gia cc doanh nghip v Trng i hc in lc nhm hng ti mc tiu to ra nhng gi tr bn vng cho x hi, TS Dng Trung Kin nhn mnh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ng thi, tin tng vi s hp tc ca cc doanh nghip s gp phn h tr cho ngi hc nng cao cht lng hc tp, pht trin ton din v chun b hnh trang tt nht cho tng lai sau khi ra trng.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>TS. Dng Trung Kin cng&nbsp;thng tin v&nbsp;tim nng pht trin chng trnh hp tc gia cc doanh nghip trong cc lnh vc o to (k thut, in, c kh...) c s ng thun o to gia cc trng i hc ti Nht Bn, i Loan v p ng nhu cu chuyn mn t cc doanh nghip quc t tuyn dng vic lm.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ti bui l, i din cc doanh nghip k bin bn ghi nh&nbsp;hp tc vi Trng i hc in lc trong cng tc o to v cung ng ngun nhn lc cht lng cao by t mong mun ng hnh cng Nh trng&nbsp;trin khai cc chng trnh h tr sinh vin thc tp, nhn hc bng v mang li c hi vic lm cho sinh vin. ng thi, cc doanh nghip&nbsp;khng nh nng lc chuyn mn hc tp,&nbsp;lm vic ti mi trng trong nc v quc t cho&nbsp;sinh vin.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mt s hnh nh ti L k kt:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXdOLq1zGbZqXVny1U4Vh3G19b6k6HRG9A8Cp5u5sXHwtMcm89ZCOO7C9-UWaWGN9Le1CVg7wtthT4Gru-bwC6nmMa2J-qG_iRV69LTRnBimwrPC5sH0UO6JhrvAYqExlonZg94wRw?key=fKQJm8HDt4tBe727O_QarXFf\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXdnvYOuAa1FfOnQHMr5i33jE-lucSD_-M7VeLVX2rbleAv2awyOYKYrcA18Bs5QMjDGnax1Yp1AjF3iyKLBf0NYan1dgBn-rmetTDZ2SUDjX7RMEOVEF3ebSVdhWxxbRSJbrwaeuQ?key=fKQJm8HDt4tBe727O_QarXFf\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXd1BFod40EgXfCYejGnhch3Bx5sjWEsLV7O3U8xeP5sfHA8L4yz0j8PzUjy_PUdffDn_H_XLs_ZxieO2wx2jNFX6WnV2vNTvl_pRpa3YWBgEjqQP31hVm1ZRFzo_vvRCSy8ukolgA?key=fKQJm8HDt4tBe727O_QarXFf\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXdKmt6RN4krSwAdqTKwwQEy8N2D6V4bmqc-RV0r8yRKvAeb358p4qtaLcOEOoLEhGXCdK75sTJ7KRXYXbhhQzpgtB6Jo8E3KTbNab5kev0kVoytGHHek1-03QfHVqIPviFE0IcIfA?key=fKQJm8HDt4tBe727O_QarXFf\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXc7xDCVDP1yj8-QwrwkmX6e4hs1cdQFUxjw-BrrgwUTYcRbJ96z47n0Rus5X-cwsu9zCaD7_Ohc8gBolAg7QY1oIiifgK8o2bKYnvp-bb-ZrigsGxekLX2XEb4oiX5rc7msWPY8Eg?key=fKQJm8HDt4tBe727O_QarXFf\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bui l k kt bin bn ghi nh hp tc gia Trng i hc in lc v cc&nbsp;doanh nghip m ra nhiu&nbsp;c hi hc tp v vic lm cho sinh vin EPU&nbsp;trong v ngoi nc.&nbsp;ng thi&nbsp;gia tng c hi nghin cu v ng dng cng ngh hin i cho sinh vin. y cng&nbsp;l cu ni cho sinh vin tip cn mi trng lm vic chuyn nghip v ng gp vai tr ca Nh trng vo s pht trin ca hi nhp quc t.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXdLxnl1npGW07uMu3KGmyn3tyaTDJJNhUtBr47V1j_PMt_yFx4x9Ql7uvwEcENMD-h71N3Xq3rOmPe1kZ2VD4C0ihUx_bw83_O93ZCDvneLzD-1xsIoNQmxvN-B0ZvkRYTnzBD9?key=fKQJm8HDt4tBe727O_QarXFf\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Cc i biu chp nh lu nim ti L k kt.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'EPUhp tc vidoanh nghipcung ng ngun nhn lc cht lng cao', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'epu-hop-tac-voi-doanh-nghiep-cung-ung-nguon-nhan-luc-chat-luong-cao', '', '', '2025-03-28 02:25:39', '2025-03-28 02:25:39', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tintucedu/?p=29', 0, 'post', '', 0),
