(35, 1, '2025-03-28 02:30:04', '2025-03-28 02:30:04', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Trng i hc in lc cng b phng n tuyn sinh i hc chnh quy nm 2025. Theo , nm nay, tng ch tiu tuyn sinh ca nh trng d kin l 6.800 ch tiu cho 32 ngnh hc, tng 13 ngnh hc v tng khong 2.800 ch tiu.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vi khong 6.800 ch tiu i hc chnh quy, nm 2025 Trng i hc in lc  m thm nhiu ngnh hc mi v: K thut ht nhn, vt liu bn dn v vi mch</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Theo , nm 2025, Trng i hc in lc tuyn sinh i hc theo 4 phng thc: Xt tuyn da trn kt qu hc tp THPT ca th sinh (xt tuyn hc b); xt tuyn kt hp da trn chng ch ting Anh quc t kt hp vi kt qu hc tp (hc b) 2 mn cn li trong t hp xt tuyn; xt tuyn da vo kt qu ca th sinh trong k thi tt nghip THPT nm 2025 do B Gio dc v o to t chc; xt tuyn thng theo quy nh trong quy ch tuyn sinh hin hnh ca B Gio dc v o to.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trng i hc in lc l trng i hc cng lp trc thuc B Cng Thng. Nh trng  ra l trnh v mc tiu pht trin: L trng i hc cng lp a ngnh, o to ngun nhn lc cht lng cao; nghin cu khoa hc, pht trin cng ngh, t vn chnh sch, chuyn giao tri thc, c bit trong lnh vc nng lng, gp phn xy dng, pht trin t nc v hi nhp quc t.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nhng nm trc, nh trng tp trung tuyn sinh cho 19 ngnh o to bc i hc, trong , hn 2/3 l chng trnh o to thuc lnh vc cng ngh, k thut. T nm 2025, s ngnh o to ca Trng i hc in lc tng ln 32 ngnh, trong , c nhiu ngnh mi p ng yu cu pht trin ca t nc trong k nguyn mi nh: Khoa hc d liu, tr tu nhn to, robot, k thut my tnh, vt liu bn dn v vi mch, cng ngh  t... c bit, bt u t nm 2025, nh trng m li ngnh o to k thut ht nhn v t chc tuyn sinh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nm 2025, Trng i hc in lc  m thm 13 ngnh o to mi, trong , c nhiu ngnh ngh ang c x hi v ngi hc quan tm, nhu cu th trng lao ng c d bo s tng trong thi gian ti i vi nhng ngnh hc nh: Cng ngh vy liu bn dn v vi mch; k thut robot; cng ngh k thut ht nhn; k thut nhit</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chi tit phng n, ngnh hc, ch tiu tuyn sinh xem&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://epu.edu.vn/Uploads/files/HCQT%20-%20File/654-%20Thong%20bao%20phuong%20an%20tuyen%20sinh%20Dai%20h%E1%BB%8Dc%20chinh%20quy%20nam%202025.pdf\">ti y.</a></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thng tin lin lc</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Phng Qun l&nbsp;o to, b phn tuyn sinh, tng 1, nh B, Trng i hc in lc, s 235 Hong Quc Vit, Phng C Nhu 1, Qun Bc T Lim, H Ni</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>in thoi: 024 2245 2662</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cng thng tin tuyn sinh: www.tuyensinh.epu.edu.vn</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Trng i hc in lc cng b phng n tuyn sinh nm 2025', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'truong-dai-hoc-dien-luc-cong-bo-phuong-an-tuyen-sinh-nam-2025', '', '', '2025-03-28 02:30:06', '2025-03-28 02:30:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tintucedu/?p=35', 0, 'post', '', 0),
